widgets_values: You can ask me to perform various tasks such as setting reminders, sending emails, making phone calls, or even answering questions. For example, you might say "Set a reminder for my doctor's appointment on Thursday at 3 PM," or "Send an email to John Doe with the subject 'Meeting Agenda'" or "Call the number 555-1234". I can also help answer questions on a wide range of topics. What would you like me to do?
